📊 Day 1 - Sales Dashboard (Power BI)
 Overview
This is my first Power BI dashboard. I created this project using my own creativity and design ideas.

 What I Did
- Created KPI cards (Total Sales, Quantity, Average Sales)
- Built bar chart to compare product sales
- Built pie chart to see category distribution
- Added slicer to filter data by region

🔹 Design

- I arranged visuals in a clean and simple layout
- Used my own color combination
- Focused on making the dashboard easy to understand

🔹 Tools Used
- Power BI

- Excel 


